opentracing-cpp
------------------------------------------
C++ implementation of the OpenTracing API

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.3.6-1
  libgcc1-11.3.0-1
  libopentracing1-1.6.0-1bl2
  libstdc++6-11.3.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.39-1
  cmake-3.23.2-1
  cygport-0.35.4-1
  gcc-core-11.3.0-1
  gcc-g++-11.3.0-1
  ninja-1.11.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/opentracing/opentracing-cpp

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/opentracing/opentracing-cpp/archive/refs/tags/v1.6.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack opentracing-cpp-1.6.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./opentracing-cpp-1.6.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/opentracing-cpp-1.6.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/opentracing-cpp-1.6.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libopentracing1-1.6.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libopentracing-devel-1.6.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

